WEBVTT

00:16:58.240 --> 00:17:03.496
What if we could track the activities
and the comings and goings

00:17:03.520 --> 00:17:05.336
of criminals who commit crimes?

00:17:05.359 --> 00:17:07.720
Just like people track
every aspect of our lives.

00:17:09.040 --> 00:17:13.455
In 2015, the Obama White House

00:17:13.480 --> 00:17:16.096
and the US Department of Justice

00:17:16.119 --> 00:17:21.136
put the number of untested,
abandoned rape kits at 400,000,

00:17:21.160 --> 00:17:22.616
across this country.

00:17:22.640 --> 00:17:24.296
Four hundred thousand.

00:17:24.319 --> 00:17:26.480
That's a national pandemic.

00:17:27.280 --> 00:17:29.496
We know where a lot of those kits are.

00:17:29.520 --> 00:17:31.216
Our testing showed